		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Could you possibly add the ability to load an external 192-byte palette file (not the 16 NES values, but the actual RGB values)? The one you included has some pretty glaring inaccuracies: $2C and $3C are almost identical, $3D has a pinkish hue, $x8 is way too orange, and $29 is way too bright. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_sad.gif" alt=":(" title="Sad" />
<br />
<br />Aside from that, this is an excellent program!

		

